---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
import { PHONE, PHONE_HREF, LICENSE_NUMBER, PROVIDER_FIRST_NAME } from "../consts";
---

<Layout
	title="About J&K Daycare | Bilingual, Montessori-Inspired Child Care in Springfield, MA"
	description="Meet Magaly — a bilingual (English/Spanish), Montessori-inspired family child care for children ages 2–5 in East Forest Park, Springfield, MA (01118)."
	pubDate={new Date("June 1, 2026")}
	heroImage="/about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		J&amp;K Daycare is a small, licensed <strong>bilingual (English &amp; Spanish)</strong> family
		child care in the East Forest Park neighborhood of Springfield, MA. We care for a small group of
		up to six children ages 2–5 in a warm home setting — so every child gets real attention,
		consistent routines, and a place that feels like a second home.
	</p>

	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>{PROVIDER_FIRST_NAME}</strong>, the licensed provider. Our approach is{" "}
		<strong>Montessori-inspired</strong> and eclectic — we blend Montessori materials with
		play-based, hands-on learning: sensory play, early literacy and math, music and movement, outdoor
		time, and nutritious meals and snacks included every day. Children grow up hearing and using both
		English and Spanish. Our staff are CPR &amp; First-Aid certified, and we're licensed by the
		Massachusetts Department of Early Education &amp; Care (EEC), license #{LICENSE_NUMBER}.
	</p>

	<p>
		We'd love to meet your family. Call <a href={PHONE_HREF}>{PHONE}</a> to schedule a tour, or{" "}
		<a href="/#tour">request a tour online</a> and we'll follow up with details and current
		availability.
	</p>
</Layout>
